uage phonology\">Phonology</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Second_language_writing\" title=\"Second language writing\">Writing</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Learners</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Multilingualism\" title=\"Multilingualism\">Multilingualism</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Heritage_language_learning\" title=\"Heritage language learning\">Heritage language</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Multi-competence\" title=\"Multi-competence\">Multi-competence</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Learner language</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Contrastive_analysis\" title=\"Contrastive analysis\">Contrastive analysis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Contrastive_rhetoric\" title=\"Contrastive rhetoric\">Contrastive rhetoric</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Error_(linguistics)\" title=\"Error (linguistics)\">Error (linguistics)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Error_analysis_(linguistics)\" title=\"Error analysis (linguistics)\">Error analysis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Error_treatment_(linguistics)\" title=\"Error treatment (linguistics)\">Error treatment</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Interlanguage_fossilization\" title=\"Interlanguage fossilization\">Fossilization</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Interlanguage\" title=\"Interlanguage\">Interlanguage</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Silent_period\" title=\"Silent period\">Silent period</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Linguistic factors</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Language_transfer\" title=\"Language transfer\">Language transfer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Linguistic_universal\" title=\"Linguistic universal\">Linguistic universal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Word_lists_by_frequency\" title=\"Word lists by frequency\">Word lists by frequency</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Individual_variation_in_second_language_acquisition\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Individual variation in second language acquisition\">Individual variation</a></th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Language-learning aptitude</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Critical_period_hypothesis\" title=\"Critical period hypothesis\">Critical period hypothesis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Motivation_in_second-language_learning\" title=\"Motivation in second-language learning\">Motivation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Willingness_to_communicate\" title=\"Willingness to communicate\">Willingness to communicate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Foreign_language_anxiety\" title=\"Foreign language anxiety\">Foreign language anxiety</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Metalinguistic_awareness\" title=\"Metalinguistic awareness\">Metalinguistic awareness</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Strategies</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Language_learning_strategies\" title=\"Language learning strategies\">Language learning strategies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Communication_strateg